✓ ProviderOrderId unique

✓ Status transitions validated

✓ Cashback configurable

✓ Balance updated only on approval

✓ Financial transactions recorded

✓ Duplicate webhook protected

✓ Idempotent processing

✓ Reversal supported

✓ Ownership from Sub1

✓ Audit trail maintained

Financial correctness is more important than performance.
